cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is about optimizing deep neural networks for embedded platforms, specifically targeting multi-objective optimization of execution time, energy consumption, and classification accuracy. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AR (Augmented Reality). Additionally, since the paper discusses the use of automated neural-architecture search (NAS) algorithms, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely sub-category. Finally, since the paper deals with hardware characteristics and optimization, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible sub-category as well.
